# Utilities-for-PDE-Toolbox-MATLAB
Easy coefficients and geometry for PDE toolbox. There are two sub-projects.

***

## Easy extraction of PDE coefficients
See [this video](www.youtube.com/embed/uVjWw9dwsCA) to get started.
To use the 'pde coefficients' app, Symbolic Math Toolbox is required.
***
## Easy creation of PDE geometry.
Start with this [README](https://github.com/deepakramas/Utilities-for-PDE-Toolbox-MATLAB/blob/master/pdetbplusExamples/html/README.html).
